  "changenote" "v2.7.0 — Two-Layer Wave System + Solo Fix + Day-Length Scaling\n\n• NEW: Two-layer wave system — surge waves crash + baseline tide runs constantly (no more silence between waves)\n• NEW: Siege duration scales with PZ day length (2-hour days = proportionally longer sieges)\n• FIX: Solo play completely overhauled — zombies now path properly in singleplayer\n• FIX: Zombies no longer die on their own in solo (CorpseSanity false positives fixed)\n• FIX: Removed AllowRepathDelay crash in solo\n• FIX: Custom sound/groan disabled (no sound assets shipped yet)\n• FIX: Stuck culling disabled in solo to prevent kill counter racing\n• Cooldowns between waves scale with day length (longer days = longer siege)\n• Solo wave pacing: steady spawns over 30+ seconds per wave (scales with day length)\n• Mini-hordes disabled by default"
